## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ANX005 Annexon Biosciences 2024 Phase 3** = first complement C1q inhibitor + GBS Phase 3. classical complement pathway 첫 GBS 표적. quantum-VQE 의 C1q hexamer + IgG-Fc binding pocket modeling fit. paradigm shift — IVIg/PE 후 첫 disease-modifying.
2. **IVIg + plasmapheresis 1980s+** = GBS standard of care 30+ years. mechanism = polyclonal IgG saturation + immunoadsorption — quantum-VQE 의 polyclonal Fab repertoire modeling 한정.
3. **corticosteroid Cochrane 2017 negative** = methylprednisolone 단독 + IVIg 병용 모두 effect 무. autoimmune-paradigm 기본 대비 GBS 의 unique exception.
4. **imlifidase Idefirix 2022 EU** = IdeS IgG cleaving enzyme — kidney transplant desensitization first. GBS research extension (cross-myasthenia_specific). single-dose IgG cleavage = 양자-VQE 의 enzyme catalytic pocket.
5. **efgartigimod Vyvgart 2021 + rozanolixizumab Rystiggo 2023** = FcRn antagonist gMG approved. GBS research extension paradigm. FcRn-IgG endosomal recycling 차단 = systemic IgG 감소. quantum-VQE 의 FcRn pocket fit.
6. **eculizumab + ravulizumab + crovalimab C5** = JET-GBS Japan pilot + research. C5 vs C1q 의 complement pathway 위치 차이 = ANX005 의 selectivity advantage (terminal C5b-9 보존).
7. **anti-ganglioside (GM1/GD1a AMAN + GQ1b MFS)** = post-Campylobacter molecular mimicry. quantum-VQE 의 antibody-glycan epitope modeling 한정 — carbohydrate flexibility 가 quantum protein-only 의 limit.
8. **Schwann cell + node of Ranvier** = AIDP 의 demyelination 표적 / AMAN 의 axonal node 표적. NRG1 / GDNF / IGF-1 trophic factor 가 repair pathway. quantum-VQE 의 ErbB receptor pocket fit.
9. **mechanical ventilation 25-30% + dysautonomia 70%** = ICU + supportive care 가 mortality 의 핵심. cross-critical_care + emergency_medicine + venous_thromboembolism + rehabilitation + chronic_fatigue 의 5+ cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, GBS 임상 의미 한정. 1976 swine flu vaccine GBS lessons + COVID-19 vaccine GBS signal = vaccinology + biosecurity_pivot 의 cross.

